  <p><anchor n="T.50.2062.0910b21"/><lb ed="T" n="0910b21"/><persName key="A008276">釋紹宗</persName>別號<persName key="A008276">遂初</persName>。<placeName key="PL000000008391">上海</placeName>陳氏子。<date key="j22141462214510" from-iso="1350-01-09" to-iso="1351-01-08">年十三</date>父母<lb ed="T" n="0910b22"/>捨入里之<placeName key="PL000000008380">安國寺</placeName>。得法於<persName key="A008279">靜庵鎮法師</persName>。天資<lb ed="T" n="0910b23"/>頴悟戒行精嚴。初出說法於杭之<placeName key="PL000000011472">長慶寺</placeName>。大<lb ed="T" n="0910b24"/>展玄風緇素嚮化。次遷吳興<placeName key="PL000000012976">慈感寺</placeName>。時金<lb ed="T" n="0910b25"/>陵<placeName key="PL000000008825">長干</placeName><persName key="A008280">守仁法師</persName>延居第一座。一眾傾伏。<date from-iso="1393-02-20" key="j22298942230247" to-iso="1394-02-08">洪<lb ed="T" n="0910b26"/>武癸酉</date>應召有事<placeName key="PL000000018775">廬山</placeName>。奏對稱　　旨賜<lb ed="T" n="0910b27"/><persName key="A008276">金縷僧伽黎</persName>。擢右講經。無何陞右善世。<date key="j22313452231345" when-iso="1397-02-10">丁<lb ed="T" n="0910b28"/>丑正月五日</date>示微疾端坐而化　　上聞勅<lb ed="T" n="0910b29"/>遣中使致祭。荼毘日送者數千人徒眾奉<lb ed="T" n="0910c01"/>收舍利遺骨塔于<placeName key="PL000000008380">安國寺</placeName>。</p>
